fno.png&h=f4f33a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCDXv4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCDXv4t.jpg&h=c2140d08&s={SIZE}\" /> </div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4.追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>七區集會</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n  日期：8月5日<br />\n  時間：下午一時開始<br />\n各區地點：金鐘添馬公園、旺角麥花臣球場、沙田百步梯、大埔廣福球場、荃灣沙咀道球場、黃大仙廣場、屯門公園<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLCv36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLCv36.jpg&h=09ba4839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKejKpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKejKpu.jpg&h=f51b4d73&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c5ce5ad1ef815ecda2864153aa7919d20c077c9d","tid":1381271,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ccdd2fbf34f97a1ed7115f54a778cf36807f7dc","tid":1381271,"uid":212182,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:57:54.000Z","msg":"[公投] 8.4 遍地開花-罷工前夕-七區集會 暨 港島西&amp;新界東夾擊大遊行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381144</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"多謝手足幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2174b2c8f93b3d966e4610b9adca847d61ccbc8b","tid":1381271,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"35b38c76608e6d170af93edf93dd3723035c95dc","tid":1381271,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:02:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b5